 decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-14-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom with glass doors, marble walls, and floor. A toilet is visible on the left, and a planter with green foliage is on the right.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-14-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567766\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567766\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Luxurious bathroom with marble walls, a lighted onyx sink, oval mirror, and vertical light fixtures. Glass shower on the left with a dark wood accent wall framing the wash area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567767\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567767\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Illuminated marble sink with a chrome faucet and soap dispenser, set against a marbled wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-16-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-16-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-16-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-16-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA multifunctional room, which Mayer refers to as “the room of uncertain function,” currently serves as Koshulynskyy’s office but is designed to adapt easily into a nursery or additional living space as needed. This flexibility reflects the couple’s foresight in creating a home that evolves with them.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567768\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567768\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-17-810x980.jpg\" alt=\"Luxurious walk-in closet with marble floor, featuring shelves of shoes and bags, clothing racks with coats and dresses, a full-length mirror, and a folded chair.\" width=\"810\" height=\"980\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-17-810x980.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-17-800x968.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-17-768x929.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-17-1269x1536.jpg 1269w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCompleted in just six and a half months, KM Home embodies the essence of modern minimalism, where every element serves a purpose, and every detail contributes to a cohesive environment that’s “for the soul.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567769\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567769\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-18-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Bathroom with white and black marble walls and floor, a wooden vanity with a dark marble countertop, large mirror, and frosted glass doors.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-18-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-18-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-18-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-18-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"attachment_567770\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=567770\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-567770\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-19-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Woman with long red hair sitting on a white couch, wearing a white top and green pants, next to a gray cat. Behind her, a large abstract painting with blue and beige tones is on the wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-19-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-19-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/01/KM-Home-Lviv-Ukraine-Koshulynskyy-Mayer-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eKarina Mayer, founder and designer of KOSHULYNSKYY \u0026amp; MAYER\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information, visit \u003ca href=\"https://kmdesignlab.com/en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003ekmdesignlab.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/bezuglov/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eAndriy Bezuglov\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
